template_id: openagreements-restrictive-covenant-wyoming
name: OpenAgreements Employee Restrictive Covenant (Wyoming)
category: non-compete
description: >-
  Wyoming-specific employee restrictive covenant agreement with modular covenant structure
  (non-compete, non-solicitation, non-dealing, non-investment, confidentiality, non-disparagement).
  Incorporates Wyo. Stat. section 1-23-108 (SF 107, 2025) pathway gating for non-compete-adjacent
  covenants. Drafted as a starting point for review by licensed counsel.
